      "source": [
        "ep = math.sqrt(235/fy)\n",
        "crf = 9*ep\n",
        "crw = 28*ep\n",
        "cw = d\n",
        "c1 = cw/tw\n",
        "cf = (b-tw-2*r)/2\n",
        "c2 = cf/tf"
      ],
      "id": "44ac1e01",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#\n",
        "# Section Classification\n",
        "\n",
        "According to EN 1993-1-1:2022 Eq 5.1, $\\epsilon$ = $\\sqrt{\\frac{235}{f_{y}}}$ = `{python} ep` \n",
        "\n",
        "\\begin{multicols}{2}\n",
        "\\begin{description}\n",
        "  \\item[]$c_{w}$ = $\\frac{(b-t_{w}-2\\cdot r)}{2}$ = `{python} cw`  \n",
        "  \\item[] $\\frac{c_{w}}{t_{w}}$ = `{python} c1`\n",
        "  \\item[]Class 1 limit for web, 72 $\\epsilon $ = `{python} crw`\n",
        "  \\item[]$c_{f}$ = $h_{w}$ = `{python} cf` \n",
        "  \\item[]$\\frac{c_{f}}{t_{f}}$ = `{python} c2`\n",
        "  \\item[]Class 1 limit for flange, 9 $\\epsilon$ = `{python} crf`\n",
        "\\end{description}  \n",
        "\\end{multicols}\n",
        "\n",
        "Since `{python} c1` < `{python} crw` and `{python} c2` < `{python} crf`, the section belongs to class 1  "
      ],
      "id": "c47b487b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "def buckle (Lcr, I, E, A, fy, a):\n",
        "  Ncr = (math.pi**2 * E * I) / ((Lcr)**2)*1e-3\n",
        "  lam = math.sqrt(( A*fy / (Ncr*1e3) ))\n",
        "  phi = 0.5*(1 + a*(lam - 0.2) + lam**2)\n",
        "  chi = min(1/(phi + math.sqrt(phi**2 - lam**2)),1)\n",
        "  return Ncr, lam, phi, chi\n",
        "\n",
        "Lcr = H\n",
        "Ncry, lamy, phiy, chiy = buckle(Lcr, Iy, E, A, fy, ay)\n",
        "Ncrz, lamz, phiz, chiz = buckle(Lcr, Iz, E, A, fy, az)\n",
        "\n",
        "gamma1 = 1.0\n",
        "chi = min([chiy,chiz])\n",
        "Nrd = chi*A*fy*1e-3/gamma1\n",
        "from IPython.display import Latex\n",
        "if Nrd > Ned:\n",
        "    output_axial = 'the section is safe in resisting axial load'\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    output_axial = 'the section is not safe in resisting axial load'"
      ],
      "id": "55ef992e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# Buckling resistance about y-y axis\n",
        "\n",
        "\\begin{description}\n",
        "  \\item[]$L_{cr,y}$ = `{python} Lcr` mm\n",
        "  \\item[]$N_{cr,y}$ = $\\frac{\\pi^{2}\\cdot E\\cdot I_{y}}{{L_{cr,y}}^{2}}$ = `{python} Ncry` kN\n",
        "  \\item[]$\\lambda_{y}$ =  $\\sqrt{\\frac{N_{Rk}}{N_{cr,y}}}$ = $\\sqrt{\\frac{A\\cdot f_{y}}{N_{cr,y}}}$ = `{python} lamy` --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Eq 8.69)\n",
        "  \\item[]$\\frac{h}{b}$ = `{python} ratio` < 1.2\n",
        "  \\item[]$t_{f}$ = `{python} tf` mm < 100~mm\n",
        "  \\item[]Use buckling curve B,  $\\alpha_{y}$ = `{python} ay` --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Table 8.2)\n",
        "  \\item[]$\\phi_{y}$ = $0.5 \\cdot (1 + \\alpha_{y} \\cdot (\\lambda_{y} - 0.2) + {\\lambda_{y}}^{2})$ = `{python} phiy` --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Eq 8.74)\n",
        "  \\item[]$\\chi_{y}$ = $\\frac{1}{\\phi_{y} + \\sqrt{{\\phi_{y}}^{2} - {\\lambda_{y}}^{2}}}$ = `{python} chiy` --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Eq 8.73)\n",
        "\\end{description}\n",
        "\n",
        "{{< pagebreak >}}\n",
        "\n",
        "#\n",
        "# Buckling resistance about z-z axis\n",
        "\\begin{description}\n",
        "  \\item[]$L_{cr,z}$ = `{python} Lcr` mm\n",
        "  \\item[]$N_{cr,z}$ = $\\frac{\\pi^{2}\\cdot E\\cdot I_{z}}{{L_{cr,z}}^{2}}$ = `{python} Ncrz` kN\n",
        "  \\item[]$\\lambda_{z}$ = $\\sqrt{\\frac{N_{Rk}}{N_{cr,z}}}$ = $\\sqrt{\\frac{A\\cdot f_{y}}{N_{cr,z}}}$ = `{python} lamz` --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Eq 8.69)\n",
        "  \\item[]$\\frac{h}{b}$ = `{python} ratio` < 1.2\n",
        "  \\item[]$t_{f}$ = `{python} tf` mm < 100~mm\n",
        "  \\item[]Use buckling curve C,  $\\alpha_{z}$ = `{python} az` --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Table 8.2)\n",
        "  \\item[]$\\phi_{z}$ = $0.5 \\cdot (1 + \\alpha_{z} \\cdot (\\lambda_{z} - 0.2) + {\\lambda_{z}}^{2})$ = `{python} phiz` --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Eq 8.74)\n",
        "  \\item[]$\\chi_{z}$ = $\\frac{1}{\\phi_{z} + \\sqrt{{\\phi_{z}}^{2} - {\\lambda_{z}}^{2}}}$ = `{python} chiz` --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Eq 8.73)\n",
        "  \n",
        "\\end{description}\n",
        "  \n",
        "# Axial load resistance\n",
        "\\begin{description}\n",
        "  \\item[]$\\chi$ = min($\\chi_{y},\\chi_{z}$) = `{python} chi`\n",
        "  \\item[]$N_{RD}$ = $\\chi\\cdot A\\cdot f_{y}$ = `{python} Nrd` kN --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Eq 8.68)\n",
        "  \\item[]$N_{ed}$ = `{python} Ned` kN.\n",
        "  \\item[]Therefore, `{python} output_axial`\n",
        "\\end{description}"
      ],
      "id": "4e5b8ef4"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Mcr = ((math.pi**2 * E * Iz) / Lcr**2) * math.sqrt(Iw/Iz + (G * It * (Lcr)**2)/ (math.pi**2 * E * It))*1e-6\n",
        "if ratio > 1.2:\n",
        "    if tf <= 40:\n",
        "        alt = min(0.12*math.sqrt(Wey/Wez), 0.34)\n",
        "    else:\n",
        "        alt = min(0.16*math.sqrt(Wey/Wez), 0.49)\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    alt = min(0.16*math.sqrt(Wey/Wez), 0.49)\n",
        "\n",
        "phi_lt = 0.5*(1 + alt*(min(lamy,lamz) - 0.2) + min(lamy,lamz)**2)\n",
        "chi_lt = min(1/(phi_lt + math.sqrt(phi_lt**2 - min(lamy,lamz)**2)),1)\n",
        "\n",
        "Myrk = Wpy*fy*1e-6\n",
        "Mzrk = Wpz*fy*1e-6\n",
        "Mbrd = chi_lt*Myrk/gamma1\n",
        "Mcrdz = Mzrk/gamma1\n",
        "\n",
        "if Mbrd > Myed and Mcrdz > Mzed:\n",
        "    output_moment = 'the section is safe in resisting bending'\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    output_moment = 'the section is not safe in resisting bending'\n",
        "\n",
        "int_ratio = Ned/Nrd + Myed/Mbrd + Mzed/Mcrdz\n",
        "if int_ratio < 1.0:\n",
        "    output_interaction = 'the result is less than 1, the section is safe in resisting interaction'\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    output_interaction = 'the result is greater than 1, the section is not safe in resisting interaction'"
      ],
      "id": "18e877e5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "{{< pagebreak >}}\n",
        "\n",
        "#\n",
        "# Lateral torsional buckling check\n",
        "\\begin{description}\n",
        "    \\item[]Critical moment, $M_{cr}$= $\\frac{\\pi^{2} \\cdot E \\cdot I_{z}}{L_{cr}^{2}} \\cdot \\left( \\frac{I_{w}}{I_{z}} + \\frac{G \\cdot I_{t} \\cdot L_{cr}^{2}}{\\pi^{2} \\cdot E \\cdot I_{t}} \\right)$ = `{python} Mcr` kNm\n",
        "    \\item[]For $\\frac{h}{b}$ > 1.2 and $t_{f}$ <= 40 mm, \n",
        "    \\item[]$\\alpha_{LT}$ = $\\min(0.12\\cdot \\sqrt{\\frac{W_{el,y}}{W_{el,z}}}, 0.34)$ = `{python} alt` --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Table 8.5)\n",
        "    \\item[]$\\phi_{LT}$ = $0.5\\cdot(1 + \\alpha_{LT}\\cdot(\\lambda_z - 0.2) + \\lambda_z^{2})$ = `{python} phi_lt` --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Eq 8.82)\n",
        "    \\item[]$\\chi_{LT}$ = $\\min(\\frac{1}{\\phi_{LT} + \\sqrt{\\phi_{LT}^{2} - \\lambda_z^{2}}},1)$ = `{python} chi_lt` --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Eq 8.81)\n",
        "    \\item[]Moment resistance (y-axis), $M_{brd}$ = $\\frac{\\chi_{LT} \\cdot W_{pl,y} \\cdot f_{y}}{\\gamma_1}$ = `{python} Mbrd` kNm --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Eq 8.79)\n",
        "    \\item[]Design moment about y-axis, $M_{yed}$ = `{python} Myed` kNm\n",
        "    \\item[]Moment resistance (z-axis), $M_{crd,z}$ = $\\frac{W_{pl,z} \\cdot f_{y}}{\\gamma_1}$ = `{python} Mcrdz` kNm --- (EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Eq 8.20)\n",
        "    \\item[]Design moment about z-axis, $M_{zed}$ = `{python} Mzed` kNm\n",
        "    \\item[]Therefore, `{python} output_moment`\n",
        "\\end{description}\n",
        "\n",
        "# Axial and bending interaction check\n",
        "\\begin{description}\n",
        "    \\item[]Assume simple construction and refer to EN 1993-1-1 :2022, Eq 8.59 \n",
        "    \\item[]$\\frac{N_{ed}}{N_{rk}} + \\frac{M_{y}}{M_{brd}} + \\frac{M_{z}}{M_{cr,dz}}$ = `{python} int_ratio`\n",
        "    \\item[]Therefore, `{python} output_interaction`\n",
        "\\end{description}\n"
      ],
      "id": "6a1f13a5"
